title: VarioPSU 24V/30W IP20
description: 1 channel LED driver from KGP Electronics GmbH with 24 V constant voltage and a maximum output power of 30 W. Type of protection IP20, class II power unit with an input voltage range of 220 – 240 V AC. Dimensions (L x W x H): 300 mm x 30 mm x 16 mm. Not dimmable. Product on secondary side dimmable with IN.finite™ controller range.
